<task id="task-5088" class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">Request a trial Visual Testing Professional</title><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><context class="- topic/section task/context ">To request a trial, follow these steps:</context><steps class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Sign in to <xref href="https://testops.katalon.io/login" scope="external" class="- topic/xref ">Katalon TestOps</xref>.</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Select the desired Account.</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click on the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Settings</uicontrol> icon and select <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Subscription Management</uicontrol>.</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Additional Products</uicontrol> section, click on the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Trial</uicontrol> button of <ph conkeyref="name-variables/visual-testing" class="- topic/ph "/>.</cmd><stepxmp class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepxmp "><image width="700" href="Additional_Product_section.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">Additional products section</alt></image></stepxmp></step></steps><result class="- topic/section task/result ">You then can automatically use a trial VTP for 30 days. </result></taskbody></task>